**Home Loan Protection Plan (HLPP)** is a decreasing term insurance that covers your outstanding home loan amount. If you pass away during the loan tenure, the insurance pays off the remaining loan so your family does not lose the house. Premium is typically 0.3–0.5% of the loan amount annually. This calculator estimates the premium and decides if HLPP is worth it for your loan.
